    <description>
---

### [choco://intel-bluetooth-drivers](choco://intel-bluetooth-drivers/s=https://nuts.bcurran3.org/nuget/chocolatey/)
To use choco:// protocol URLs, install [choco:// Protocol support ](https://nuts.bcurran3.org/feeds/chocolatey/choco-protocol-support/versions)


---

Installs Intel® Wireless Bluetooth® version xx.xx.xx. Driver version varies depending on the wireless adapter installed.

